  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the effect of remote ischemic preconditioning on
      biochemical and functional indices of cardiac function induced by a 30 km run in healthy
      trained long distance runners.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
